FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

You can download the Hudsons Bay Rewards app for free from the App Store and Google Play. If you're not a Hudson's Bay Rewards member, no problem, you can join on the app.

View all your offers on the Hudsons Bay Rewards app or when you sign in to your account at thebay.com.

These are offers designed just for you. Members will receive access to 3-5 personalized offers every week from Hudsons Bay and Zellers - providing an opportunity for members to earn points even faster. Weekly personalized offers must be activated in-app or online prior to checkout.

Simply tap the Activate Now button located on each personalized offer that you want to use. Thats it! You can view and activate your personalized offers on the Hudsons Bay Rewards app or when you sign in to your account at thebay.com.

Quest offers are a series of linked milestones that, once all achieved, trigger a nice point bonus. These in-store offers are exclusive to the Hudsons Bay Rewards app. Quests can be viewed, and their progress tracked, within the app.

Receive Hudsons Bay Rewards points instantly on purchases made in-store at Hudsons Bay and Zellers. For purchases made online at thebay.com and Zellers.ca, you will receive your Hudsons Bay Rewards points within twenty-four (24) hours of the item(s) being shipped. Note that merchandise return will result in deduction of awarded points.

No, members cannot redeem points for a Hudsons Bay or Zellers gift card. Instead, members can instantly redeem their points online or in-store to save on their purchases.
